column2:
"Kirito, you seem really dissatisfied...
You're still thinking about getting your revenge, aren't you."
"Aren't you frustrated about leaving things on a defeat?"
"Of course. But I'd like us all to keep on exploring this world, too."
"Alright, then we'll make it a simple challenge. Whoever defeats the most enemies is the winner! I hope you two are prepared for this!"
